{"tid":2420319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now：德國聲稱中國試圖威嚇居德香港人","createTime":"2021-02-24T00:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T03:05:54.000Z","uid":290404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6457365ead5a966663c5628e179d607c99b44f8","tid":2420319,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】<strong>德國內政部聲稱</strong>，香港前年爆發反修例示威後，中國政府試圖威嚇居住在德國的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n《南德意志報》刊登德國內政部回覆國會人權委員會主席延森的信件。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>信中聲稱在2019年8月中，漢堡一場聲援香港示威者的集會中，有親中人士在現場拍攝集會人士，認為有可能用來威嚇相關的人。</strong>信中又指現時約有720名來自香港的人，在德國持有居留許可。<br />\n<br />\n延森接受路透社訪問時指，德國政府是時候認清中國政府派出的人員會對流亡到德國的香港人構成威脅，延森又質疑德國政府是否能夠保護這些人的安全。<br />\n<br />\n延森曾就黃之鋒等人被判刑表態，認為是顯示香港在人權和法治進入黑暗時代，<strong>中國駐柏林大使館當時批評延森的講法充滿無知和傲慢，無視客觀事實，也違背了不干涉別國內政的國際關係基本準則。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425085&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=3f41661e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425085&h=80b56365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425085</a>"},{"pid":"19939a6371894d582a516a12fd967df02b7426c7","tid":2420319,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"肥婆：我就退休，俾我奶埋先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-09-07/CLIPPING/656/A07A00_T_01_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-09-07%2FCLIPPING%2F656%2FA07A00_T_01_02.jpg&h=bbb3c937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94662fb7efe7537c36b01c4bf43d0468cf142c90","tid":2420319,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:05:54.000Z